Add and calculate a new Calculated_Date column¶

Use Day, Month, Year to create a Date column (YYYY-MM-DD)¶

In [27]:
sales['Calculated_Date'] = sales[['Year', 'Month', 'Day']].apply(lambda x: '{}-{}-{}'.format(x[0], x[1], x[2]), axis=1)
